text: Graeme English (25 September 1964 - 18 February 2021) was a Scottish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 90 kg at the 1988 Summer Olympics. He was born in Kilsyth, Scotland. English died on 18 February 2021, aged 56. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Sportspeople from North Lanarkshire Category:Olympians for Great Britain Category:Wrestlers
